    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>* BMG Direct, New York, part of the BMG Entertainment unit of Bertelsmann A.G., to Hanft Byrne Raboy &amp; Partners, New York, to introduce OnePriceCDs, which plans to sell compact discs for $9.99, including shipping and handling, from a Web site (www.onepricecds.com). Spending was estimated at $5 million.</p>
      </block>
